<h5>Join the Conexxus Team</h5><p>If you&rsquo;re a driven professional motivated by success, and you&rsquo;re looking for an opportunity to work with a rapidly expanding software company, Conexxus may be the place for you. We're always on the lookout for bright and talented people&nbsp;to addition to our team.&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Current Openings:</strong></p><p><strong>&bull;&nbsp;Business Unit Manager, Financial Institutions</strong> &#8211; Looking for a seasoned sales professional with experience in financial services and/or asset sales. Comfort with calling on financial institution executives is a must.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p><p><strong>&bull;&nbsp;Director of Business Development</strong> &#8211; Looking for an experienced individual ready to lead Conexxus in national expansion of our partner and distribution channels.&nbsp; Contract and negotiation experience appreciated but not required.</p><p>If interested in any of the&nbsp;open positions listed above, please email resume and salary requirements to <a href="mailto:careers@conexxus.com">careers@conexxus.com</a>.<br /></p>
